CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

May 26, 2010

[Cite as 05/26/2010 Case Announcements, 2010-Ohio-2212.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2009-0669. In re Application of Duke Energy Ohio, Inc.

Public Utilities Commission, Nos. 08-920-EL-SSO, 08-921-EL-AAM, 08-922-EL-UNC, and 08-923-EL-ATA. Sua sponte, this cause is dismissed for failure to present a justiciable case or controversy.

Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell, Lanzinger, and Cupp, JJ., concur. Brown, C.J., and Pfeifer, J., dissent.
